cdata.name: Esports.com
cdata.desc:
Esports.com is an Ethereum based platformwhere gamers and gaming fans are able to share, curate and enjoy content together or participate in and contribute to events. The one-stop service platform isslipt in 3 mains branches: education, entertainment, and statistics. Users can participate in creating content for these areas by writing guides or producing videos.

Esports.com platform is powered by the Esports Reward Tokens (ERT) whichis used to pay for training, acquiring in-game items, hardware merchandising, unlocking the premium subscription tiers, rewards for creating content and unlocking exclusive content.
